## Case 1: Absolute and Relative Navigation
+ /users/{ $id }: ( !^$name );
+ ./profile/bio: ( $text );
+ ../settings/theme: ( $color );

## Case 2: Digging (Xpath style)
+ //posts: ( $title, $body );
+ /forum//replies/{ $user_id }: ( $content );

## Case 3: Deep Path (Piped)
+ /catalog/{ ./category } |> //items/{ /active_user/filter }: ( $name );

## Case 4: Expressions in Path Selection
+ ./data/{ my_formula(1, 2) }: ( $result );
+ ./data/{ [ 1, 2, 3 ] }: ( $collection );
